==DFL-Supercup==
{{main|2014 DFL-Supercup}}

===DFL-Supercup review===
Bayern faced [[Borussia Dortmund]] in the [[2014 DFL-Supercup|DFL-Supercup]] on 13 August.<ref name="supercup"/> Borussia Dortmund won the match 2–0 with goals from [[Henrikh Mkhitaryan]] and [[Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang]].<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hartmann|first1=Ulrich|title=Dortmund hebt den Zeigefinger|url=http://www.sueddeutsche.de/sport/sieg-im-supercup-dortmund-hebt-den-zeigefinger-1.2088890|accessdate=13 August 2014|publisher=Süddeutsche Zeitung|date=13 August 2014|language=German}}</ref> [[Javi Martínez]] left the match injured<ref name="Dortmund dominate Bayern to claim Supercup">{{cite news|last1=Hallam|first1=Mark|title=Dortmund dominate Bayern to claim Supercup|url=http://www.dw.de/dortmund-dominate-bayern-to-claim-supercup/a-17852924|accessdate=14 August 2014|publisher=Deutsche Welle|date=13 August 2014}}</ref> after [[Anterior cruciate ligament injury|tearing his ACL]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Javi Martinez: Bayern Munich midfielder ruled out for rest of year|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28793723|accessdate=14 August 2014|publisher=BBC Sports|date=14 August 2014}}</ref> This was the third consecutive year where Bayern has faced Borussia Dortmund in the competition.<ref name="Supercup: FCB und BVB treffen sich später"/> Bayern won the [[DFL-Supercup|super cup]] in [[2012 DFL-Supercup|2012]] 2–1 and Borussia Dortmund won in [[2013 DFL-Supercup|2013]] 4–2.<ref name="Supercup: FCB und BVB treffen sich später"/> The match was originally scheduled for four days earlier.<ref name="Supercup: FCB und BVB treffen sich später">{{cite news|title=Supercup: FCB und BVB treffen sich später|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/605230/artikel_supercup_fcb-und-bvb-treffen-sich-spaeter.html|accessdate=3 June 2014|publisher=kicker|date=28 May 2014|language=German}}</ref> Bayern was without [[Thiago Alcântara|Thiago]],<ref name="Bayern Munich’s Thiago Alcântara suffers setback with knee injury"/> [[Franck Ribéry]],<ref name="Rafinha erleidet Außenbandriss - Pause für Ribery">{{cite news|title=Rafinha erleidet Außenbandriss - Pause für Ribery|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/609445/artikel_rafinha-erleidet-aussenbandriss---pause-fuer-ribery.html|accessdate=12 August 2014|publisher=kicker|date=10 August 2014|language=German}}</ref> and [[Rafinha (footballer, born 1985)|Rafinha]].<ref name="Rafinha erleidet Außenbandriss - Pause für Ribery"/> [[Sebastian Rode]], [[Gianluca Gaudino]], [[Juan Bernat]], and [[Robert Lewandowski]] made their debuts for Bayern.<ref name="Dortmund dominate Bayern to claim Supercup"/>

